my early acceptance application

148
00:06:27.095 --> 00:06:28.722  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
for Harvard.

149
00:06:28.805 --> 00:06:30.682  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I don't want to run the risk
of ending up at State.

150
00:06:30.765 --> 00:06:32.226  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Our state school
isn't bad.

151
00:06:32.309 --> 00:06:35.145  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But it's
within driving distance.

152
00:06:35.229 --> 00:06:36.897  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Did you bring the home videos
of me as a kid?

153
00:06:36.980 --> 00:06:38.315  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I need to work them
into my application.

154
00:06:38.397 --> 00:06:41.860  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I sure did.
Got a picture album too.

155
00:06:45.864 --> 00:06:47.615  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dad,
these are all black.

156
00:06:47.699 --> 00:06:50.202  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, unfortunately that's how
they've always been.

157
00:06:50.285 --> 00:06:53.205  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The camera I bought
came with this thing on the lens

158
00:06:53.288 --> 00:06:55.623  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
that totally ruined
all of our pictures.

159
00:06:55.707 --> 00:06:58.377  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
A lens cap?

160
00:06:58.459 --> 00:07:01.755  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dad, you were supposed
to take it off.

161
00:07:01.838 --> 00:07:04.299  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So we have no pictures
of me as a kid?

162
00:07:04.383 --> 00:07:05.759  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We have tons.

163
00:07:05.842 --> 00:07:09.888  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Look, here's your first
Halloween costume.

164
00:07:09.971 --> 00:07:12.349  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You can't see it,
but you're adorable.

165
00:07:12.432 --> 00:07:15.018  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
What about home videos?
Tell me I can use those.

166
00:07:15.102 --> 00:07:17.437  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You can use them,
but they're all black too.

167
00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.022  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You can hear some stuff,

168
00:07:19.106 --> 00:07:22.276  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
like Richie yelling something
about a cap thing.

169
00:07:22.359 --> 00:07:25.486  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh!

170
00:07:25.570 --> 00:07:28.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dad, I need childhood videos
to show the story of my life.

171
00:07:28.865 --> 00:07:31.368  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm so sorry
that I messed this up.

172
00:07:31.451 --> 00:07:34.955  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But my memories of you
as a little girl are so special,

173
00:07:35.038 --> 00:07:38.875  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'll bet I can re-create them
using pen and paper.

174
00:07:38.959 --> 00:07:41.044  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Hold on.
You said "re-create."

175
00:07:41.128 --> 00:07:44.005  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, why?
Is that the wrong word?

176
00:07:44.089 --> 00:07:47.592  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Is it "recreate"?
I never know the difference.

177
00:07:47.675 --> 00:07:50.929  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Maybe I can re-create
the videos and pictures.

178
00:07:51.012 --> 00:07:53.556  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
No need.
I already did.

179
00:07:53.640 --> 00:07:55.183  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
See?

180
00:07:55.267 --> 00:07:58.645  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Here I am walking you
to your first day of preschool.

181
00:07:58.728 --> 00:08:01.356  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Wow, I was skinny
back then.

182
00:08:05.026 --> 00:08:11.825  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Richie, I'm going
to make sure it's safe.

183
00:08:11.908 --> 00:08:13.660  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
All clear.

184
00:08:16.455 --> 00:08:19.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okay, so far,
so good.

185
00:08:19.374 --> 00:08:21.126  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So why are you
wearing that again?

186
00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:23.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Murray told me
to blend in.

187
00:08:24.004 --> 00:08:26.923  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You're being ridiculous.

188
00:08:29.092 --> 00:08:30.969  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
- Murray?
- Murray.

189
00:08:31.052 --> 00:08:33.638  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Look, I'm not really scared.

190
00:08:33.721 --> 00:08:35.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Master Richie,
I received the ghost spray

191
00:08:35.723 --> 00:08:38.101  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
from that witch doctor
in Aruba.

192
00:08:38.185 --> 00:08:40.895  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ghost spray?
I didn't order that.

193
00:08:40.979 --> 00:08:43.940  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Be sure to get
under my bed.

194
00:08:44.024 --> 00:08:47.402  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Come on.
There aren't any ghosts in here.

195
00:08:47.486 --> 00:08:50.113  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You have no idea
what you're dealing with.

196
00:08:50.197 --> 00:08:54.242  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I've faced these
supernatural beings before.

197
00:08:54.326 --> 00:08:57.578  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
My great-great-grandmother
haunted us for months.

198
00:08:57.662 --> 00:09:01.624  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
She kept wanting us
to try the soup.

199
00:09:01.708 --> 00:09:05.962  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
We're full, Doris!
We're full!

200
00:09:12.386 --> 00:09:15.638  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
As usual, the only abnormal
thing in this room is Murray.

201
00:09:15.722 --> 00:09:17.349  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's not haunted.

202
00:09:17.432 --> 00:09:20.227  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Maybe I was just
hearing things.

203
00:09:20.310 --> 00:09:21.602  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[echoing moan]

204
00:09:21.686 --> 00:09:22.979  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Like that.

205
00:09:23.063 --> 00:09:24.689  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What is that?

206
00:09:24.772 --> 00:09:26.107  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's the end.

207
00:09:26.191 --> 00:09:27.567  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm prepared.

208
00:09:27.650 --> 00:09:30.945  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Are you?

209
00:09:31.029 --> 00:09:32.072  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[moaning]

210
00:09:32.155 --> 00:09:33.823  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[horn honking]
[alarm sounding]

211
00:09:33.907 --> 00:09:36.326  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Irona?

212
00:09:36.410 --> 00:09:38.870  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[rumbling]
I'm out of here!

213
00:09:40.872 --> 00:09:42.541  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[moaning]

214
00:09:42.623 --> 00:09:44.543  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's locked!
What's happening?

215
00:09:44.625 --> 00:09:47.254  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I don't know.

216
00:09:47.337 --> 00:09:49.548  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hey, let me out!

217
00:09:49.630 --> 00:09:51.674  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm a ghost too!
Aah!

218
00:09:58.473 --> 00:09:59.891  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Whew!

219
00:09:59.974 --> 00:10:02.561  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Good thing I had
that secret passage put in.

220
00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:08.275  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, I guess now
it's just a passage.

221
00:10:08.358 --> 00:10:09.984  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That was crazy.

222
00:10:10.068 --> 00:10:12.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Your room is actually haunted.

223
00:10:12.446 --> 00:10:13.738  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I told you!

224
00:10:13.821 --> 00:10:17.242  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm never setting foot
in there again.

225
00:10:17.325 --> 00:10:18.535  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[laughs]

226
00:10:18.618 --> 00:10:21.788  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Hear that?
Ghost laughter.

227
00:10:21.871 --> 00:10:24.749  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No, that was me.

228
00:10:24.832 --> 00:10:27.127  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Richie, I think
I may have figured out

229
00:10:27.210 --> 00:10:28.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
why your room
is being haunted.

230
00:10:29.003 --> 00:10:31.423  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It was built
directly above a burial ground.

231
00:10:31.506 --> 00:10:34.509  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What website are you on?

232
00:10:34.593 --> 00:10:37.137  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ugh, why do people
always build stuff

233
00:10:37.220 --> 00:10:39.264  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
over Indian burial grounds?

234
00:10:39.347 --> 00:10:41.057  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No, it's much worse.

235
00:10:41.141 --> 00:10:43.643  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
This isn't
an Indian burial ground.

236
00:10:43.726 --> 00:10:46.187  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's a pilgrim burial ground.

237
00:10:46.271 --> 00:10:48.482  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, that's a refreshing
change of pace.

238
00:10:48.565 --> 00:10:50.609  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Maybe we can make peace
with these pilgrims.

239
00:10:50.691 --> 00:10:55.780  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It looks like Thanksgiving
has come early this year.

240
00:10:55.863 --> 00:10:58.032  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Who are you right now?

241
00:10:58.116 --> 00:11:02.662  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm your best chance
at staying alive.

242
00:11:03.913 --> 00:11:05.373  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cha-ching]

243
00:11:05.457 --> 00:11:06.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okay, smile,
'cause these are the books

244
00:11:07.041 --> 00:11:08.627  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
you really wanted
for Christmas.

245
00:11:08.709 --> 00:11:11.546  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
What kind of loser
wants books for Christmas?

246
00:11:11.630 --> 00:11:13.632  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Me, at eight years old.

247
00:11:16.675 --> 00:11:19.971  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
All right, I'm ready
to re-create these pictures.

248
00:11:20.054 --> 00:11:22.723  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dad, why are you dressed
like a caveman?

249
00:11:22.807 --> 00:11:25.268  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
This is what I wore
in the '90s.

250
00:11:25.352 --> 00:11:27.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Who's the little girl?

251
00:11:27.437 --> 00:11:29.356  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
That's Noah, but as far
as Harvard's concerned,

252
00:11:29.439 --> 00:11:30.857  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
she's me
at eight years old.

253
00:11:30.940 --> 00:11:33.109  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
She looks nothing like
you did.

254
00:11:33.193 --> 00:11:35.945  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
She doesn't have pigtails.
She's not sucking her thumb.

255
00:11:36.029 --> 00:11:39.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
She doesn't have that crazy
orthodontic headgear on.

256
00:11:39.616 --> 00:11:40.783  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

257
00:11:40.867 --> 00:11:42.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I had an overbite, okay?

258
00:11:42.243 --> 00:11:44.787  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
'Cause she sucked
her thumb.

259
00:11:44.871 --> 00:11:46.665  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
She still does
whenever she gets really upset.

260
00:11:46.747 --> 00:11:49.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okay, go sit
next to Noah.

261
00:11:49.792 --> 00:11:52.003  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I need a video of you
giving me my beaker set.

262
00:11:52.086 --> 00:11:54.381  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Pfft, I never gave you
a beaker set.

263
00:11:54.464 --> 00:11:56.924  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I know.
You gave me a set of bird beaks.

264
00:11:57.008 --> 00:11:59.344  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What a loser.

265
00:12:00.887 --> 00:12:02.347  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
This is
very important to me,

266
00:12:02.430 --> 00:12:05.850  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and you guys are refusing
to cooperate, and--

267
00:12:05.933 --> 00:12:08.687  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
- [chuckles]
- Told you.

268
00:12:10.647 --> 00:12:12.649  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Greetings,
pilgrim spirits.

269
00:12:12.731 --> 00:12:17.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
We are here to offer you
a homemade Thanksgiving feast.

270
00:12:17.404 --> 00:12:20.365  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Wait a minute, you didn't
say anything about homemade.

271
00:12:20.448 --> 00:12:22.992  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I just brought
some canned corn.

272
00:12:23.076 --> 00:12:24.703  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Recess is over, Richie.

273
00:12:24.785 --> 00:12:27.038  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Get it together.

274
00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:30.917  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, come on,
Richie!

275
00:12:32.377 --> 00:12:37.298  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[moaning]
[alarm sounding]

276
00:12:37.382 --> 00:12:39.551  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Great,
now you've upset them.

277
00:12:39.634 --> 00:12:41.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Quick, pull out
the pumpkin pie.

278
00:12:41.802 --> 00:12:43.346  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That's homemade, isn't it?

279
00:12:43.430 --> 00:12:44.972  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The crust is,
but the filling,

280
00:12:45.056 --> 00:12:47.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
yeah, that's canned.

281
00:12:47.308 --> 00:12:49.852  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Why didn't you have your
personal chef prepare the meal?

282
00:12:49.936 --> 00:12:53.231  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I don't make my employees
work on Thanksgiving.

283
00:12:53.314 --> 00:12:55.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[moaning]

284
00:12:55.149 --> 00:12:57.193  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Let's get out of here!

285
00:12:59.362 --> 00:13:00.947  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's locked!

286
00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:03.575  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Quick,
to the not-so-secret passage!

287
00:13:08.413 --> 00:13:11.374  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[all scream]

288
00:13:12.959 --> 00:13:14.335  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Irona is possessed.

289
00:13:14.419 --> 00:13:15.836  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
How are we
supposed to escape

290
00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.796  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
with the ghost
