00:19:50.773 --> 00:19:53.609  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okay, I will say this
as gently as possible.

436
00:19:53.693 --> 00:19:56.737  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dollar, Dollar, and Bill Y'all
hate living in your house.

437
00:19:56.821 --> 00:19:59.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That was gentle?

438
00:19:59.866 --> 00:20:02.201  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
They would prefer
to be in the ocean.

439
00:20:02.284 --> 00:20:04.370  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[moans]

440
00:20:04.453 --> 00:20:06.039  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
As much fun as they have
with you,

441
00:20:06.122 --> 00:20:08.207  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
they want to be swimming
in the open ocean.

442
00:20:08.290 --> 00:20:10.417  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
