fresh sardines are much better

443
00:20:10.501 --> 00:20:13.337  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
than the canned ones
they get here.

444
00:20:13.420 --> 00:20:14.839  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What?

445
00:20:14.922 --> 00:20:18.759  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Do you know how expensive
fresh seafood is?

446
00:20:18.843 --> 00:20:20.219  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh, Murray.

447
00:20:20.302 --> 00:20:22.221  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I feel terrible.

448
00:20:22.304 --> 00:20:24.598  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, I guess there's
only one thing for me to do.

449
00:20:24.682 --> 00:20:26.517  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Let me take
that month off?

450
00:20:26.600 --> 00:20:30.229  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's time to release
Dollar, Dollar, and Bill Y'all.

451
00:20:30.312 --> 00:20:31.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I want what's best
for them,

452
00:20:31.564 --> 00:20:33.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and if they aren't happy
with me,

453
00:20:33.524 --> 00:20:35.818  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
they don't belong here.

454
00:20:35.902 --> 00:20:37.611  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's been fun, guys.

455
00:20:37.695 --> 00:20:40.656  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
