with a new hello.

458
00:20:45.578 --> 00:20:47.038  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Good-bye, Dr. Bill.

459
00:20:47.121 --> 00:20:48.414  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hello!

460
00:20:48.497 --> 00:20:50.249  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
No, seriously,
get lost.

461
00:20:50.332 --> 00:20:51.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

462
00:20:54.128 --> 00:20:56.214  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[whale moaning] I'm going to miss Richie

463
00:20:57.048 --> 00:20:59.884  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But I won't miss the ghosts
haunting that place.

464
00:21:00.593 --> 00:21:01.802  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[rumbling]

465
00:21:01.886 --> 00:21:07.767  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[horn honking]
[alarm sounding]

466
00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:09.393  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
For reals?

467
00:21:12.646 --> 00:21:16.150  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
